method.name: dtype
method.description: Data-type of the array’s elements.

method.name: get
method.description: Indexes into the array, and return the resulting tensor.

method.name: get_bool
method.description: Indexes into the array, and return the resulting value as bool. Errors if the index does not yield a single value.

method.name: get_float
method.description: Indexes into the array, and return the resulting value as float. Errors if the index does not yield a single value.

method.name: get_int
method.description: Indexes into the array, and return the resulting value as int. Errors if the index does not yield a single value.

method.name: ndim
method.description: Number of array dimensions.

method.name: set
method.description: Indexes into the array, sets the element to the given value. The value's dimensions must match this array's last dimensions.

method.name: shape
method.description: Array of array dimensions.

method.name: size
method.description: Number of elements in the array. Equal to nd.prod(a.shape()), i.e., the product of the array’s dimensions.

method.name: to_bool
method.description: Convert this tensor to a single bool. Errors if size() is not 1.

method.name: to_float
method.description: Convert this tensor to a single float. Errors if size() is not 1.

method.name: to_godot_array
method.description: Convert this tensor to a Godot array. For now, the resulting array is flat.

method.name: to_int
method.description: Convert this tensor to a single int. Errors if size() is not 1.

method.name: to_packed_byte_array
method.description: If 1D, converts this tensor to a PackedByteArray.

method.name: to_packed_color_array
method.description: If shape is [?, 4], converts this tensor to a PackedColorArray.

method.name: to_packed_float32_array
method.description: If 1D, converts this tensor to a PackedFloat32Array.

method.name: to_packed_float64_array
method.description: If 1D, converts this tensor to a PackedFloat64Array.

method.name: to_packed_int32_array
method.description: If 1D, converts this tensor to a PackedInt32Array.

method.name: to_packed_int64_array
method.description: If 1D, converts this tensor to a PackedInt64Array.

method.name: to_packed_vector2_array
method.description: If shape is [?, 2], converts this tensor to a PackedVector2Array.

method.name: to_packed_vector3_array
method.description: If shape is [?, 3], converts this tensor to a PackedVector3Array.

method.name: to_packed_vector4_array
method.description: If shape is [?, 4], converts this tensor to a PackedVector4Array.
